FBIS4-21769 "jptot014__l94069" JPRS-TOT-94-014-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 28 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA IRAQ Defense Minister Reportedly Wounded in Murder Attempt Defense Minister Reportedly Wounded in Murder Attempt NC2803174194 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan in Arabic 1500 GMT 28 Mar 94 NC2803174194 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan in Arabic 1500 GMT 28 Mar 94 Arabic BFN [Text] AL-MU'TAMAR newspaper, mouthpiece of the Unified Iraqi National Congress, has reported that the Free Revolutionary Officers Movement has issued a statement saying that the Iraqi regime's defense minister, 'Ali Hasan al-Majid, was the target of an assassination attempt in March. The paper cites the statement as saying that members of the Revolutionary Officers Movement opened fire at al-Majid outside his house in Baghdad, wounding him in the leg and arm and killing his bodyguard Major Salih and two other guards.
